{"title":"Foldylock & CLOSCA Loop Folding Helmet get Priority Limited Edition 174HUDSON colors","link":"https://bikerumor.com/foldylock-closca-loop-folding-helmet-get-priority-limited-edition-174hudson-colors/","date":1637689670000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184644/Loop_Foldylock_174_Hudson_Lifestyle.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"410\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184644/Loop_Foldylock_174_Hudson_Lifestyle-800x410.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184644/Loop_Foldylock_174_Hudson_Lifestyle-800x410.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184644/Loop_Foldylock_174_Hudson_Lifestyle-297x152.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184644/Loop_Foldylock_174_Hudson_Lifestyle-120x61.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184644/Loop_Foldylock_174_Hudson_Lifestyle-768x393.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184644/Loop_Foldylock_174_Hudson_Lifestyle.jpg 859w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-279065\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>New York-based Priority Bicycles has rolled out a special edition, high-visibility color option to its collection of commuter-centered accessories from other brands to complement their line of belt-driven bicycles.</p><div id=\"attachment_279066\"><p><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-279066\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184642/174Hudson_Loop_Foldylock.jpg\" alt=\"Foldylock &amp; CLOSCA Loop Folding Helmet get Priority Limited Edition 174HUDSON colors\" width=\"621\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184642/174Hudson_Loop_Foldylock.jpg 621w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184642/174Hudson_Loop_Foldylock-297x192.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22184642/174Hudson_Loop_Foldylock-120x78.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px\"></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-279066\">Priority’s 174Hudson CLOSCA Loop helmet and Foldylock breaks down for easy storage.</p></div><p>The CLOSCA Loop collapsable helmet, along with the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/foldylock-forever-claims-to-be-worlds-strongest-folding-bicycle-lock/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Foldylock</a> folding bike lock, are now available in the high-visibility 174Hudson color, named after the address of Priority’s New York City showroom. The design features bright yellow detailing to grab the attention of drivers paired with a graphite grey.</p><p>Priority makes a range of&nbsp; commuter bicycles that include<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/review-priority-bicycles-gates-belt-driven-continuum-is-a-low-maintenance-commuter/\"> belt-driven drivetrains</a> at affordable prices.</p><p>The foldable helmet and lock carry that same innovative spirit. Both the helmet and lock break down for easy storage sothe&nbsp; user can hop off the bike and go about their day without lugging around bulky gear, or without having to ride with an awkward lock.</p><div id=\"attachment_279071\"><p><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-279071\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192353/174hudson_Closca_2_1of1.jpg\" alt=\"Foldylock &amp; CLOSCA Loop Folding Helmet get Priority Limited Edition 174HUDSON colors\" width=\"1444\" height=\"963\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192353/174hudson_Closca_2_1of1.jpg 1444w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192353/174hudson_Closca_2_1of1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192353/174hudson_Closca_2_1of1-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192353/174hudson_Closca_2_1of1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192353/174hudson_Closca_2_1of1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1444px) 100vw, 1444px\"></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-279071\">174Hudson CLOSCA helmet broken down.</p></div><p>The CLOSCA Loop collapses into rings that make it about half the depth when broken down compared to its ready-to-wear footprint. At 330 grams, it’s a solid option for riders who value portability over everything else. Likewise, the Foldylock folds into a compact package that can easily be mounted to a bike or tucked into a pack or pocket, while still offering protection. The lock has a Sold Secure Silver certification, which offers peace of mind to those who have to leave their bikes locked up for hours at a time.</p><div id=\"attachment_279069\"><p><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-279069\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192132/174hudson_foldylock_4_1of1_1024x1024-e1637688971819.jpg\" alt=\"Foldylock &amp; CLOSCA Loop Folding Helmet get Priority Limited Edition 174HUDSON colors\" width=\"867\" height=\"294\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192132/174hudson_foldylock_4_1of1_1024x1024-e1637688971819.jpg 867w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192132/174hudson_foldylock_4_1of1_1024x1024-e1637688971819-297x101.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192132/174hudson_foldylock_4_1of1_1024x1024-e1637688971819-800x271.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192132/174hudson_foldylock_4_1of1_1024x1024-e1637688971819-120x41.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/22192132/174hudson_foldylock_4_1of1_1024x1024-e1637688971819-768x260.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 867px) 100vw, 867px\"></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-279069\">174Hudson Foldylock folded down.</p></div><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/5SFwdZvdr8A?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;start=3&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>Both the CLOSCA Loop helmet and Foldylock are available for MSRP $79.99. However, if you act fast, you can snag a helmet for half the price during the company’s<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/get-your-early-call-up-for-holiday-savings-with-these-pre-black-friday-deals/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> Black Friday sale</a>.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=ale&amp;pw=147535&amp;mi=16029&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prioritybicycles.com%2F\" rel=\"ugc\"><em>https://www.prioritybicycles.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Mark Wilson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"848939aacf67692c11bce3664aa571320ebf61d39192d08d8236cb70ef9d7e69","category":"Cycling"}